{"tid":1377290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<極度重要>你既決定關乎於香港既未來！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:17:48.000Z","uid":82241,"like":524,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"a76ddeb232207e088feb855bec36c6a6e24a5b39","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"1.記住<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span><br />\n前線既決定 你可以唔同意但要尊重<br />\n團體合作打boss，不要落單<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">前線派</span></span>要多溝通並通知支援派<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">支援派</span></span>驚既就去和平派<br />\n唔驚既就唔好退 並支援前線派<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">和平派</span></span> 唔好立刻離場 睇下有咩可以幫支援派<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">鍵盤戰士派</span></span> 你地就最神聖 <br />\n幫手推當日最有用既五個post <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">包括裝備 位置 策略 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不包括撤退</span></span><br />\n令和平派可以用前方傳達<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攻守絕對要一致</span></span><br />\n前線派話攻既  就要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救人</span></span> 前線+支援 一齊上<br />\n守既 就一步一步<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慢慢向後撤退</span></span>至安全地方<br />\n再商討下一步既決定 守新據點定走場<br />\n千奇唔好只係退守一條街 <br />\n當你每退守一條街就會有機會令義士被捕<br />\n一條又一條街咁退 被捕人士數目就會不堪設想<br />\n令到下一步更難做決定 即係自行解體<br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如發現火種不要自行撲滅</span></span><br />\n火燭咁大件事 而且發生市民同警察中間咁危險<br />\n做市民既 當然要叫消防隊救熄啦 <br />\n我地平民百姓無受過專業訓練<br />\n萬一火勢加劇 受傷既只會係自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要食飯<br />\n我要攞毛毯</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e7bad0c0bb8d4641968aab97205dd07d0e641f3","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"依家既香港 無民意可言<br />\n亦無警察去維持秩序<br />\n都無政府去解決問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">靠既只有自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"df2e18fafce628020202ad7a0a820c8450e3d364","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"依家政府已經開左先例<br />\n以後你想遊行集會都未必得<br />\n所以各有各行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c670b5b3728bb8f8190aaaaf3712ff0a48da6eed","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"023d24b1adba5b68a780c7a6d9d559710a35c9f4","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"推啊  同我大大力推"},{"pid":"a1360dbe12c7612cc464185471c22e217ed59c04","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"推啊唔該"},{"pid":"4d3d55e673ce2aba6a724097bb2321ad2e473173","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"喂 主線任"},{"pid":"694ece1eabf1d74f0f6f3379aca5bd8516657308","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"576dd25224313edcc97931031adff8b2340fdc4f","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"幫手推依個"},{"pid":"b3309f4b7645dcc0c3a9edee3aef50cb421966a3","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"350d15954df1847aabac082a09cd422441e167f4","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"快d推先"},{"pid":"7cafc6141edf9a9e813df0f80ca4a616a5836bf8","tid":1377290,"uid":82241,"like":0