0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6110aa6a68762b4dfdea691b6d330d6fa32631e0","tid":1377290,"uid":211707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"824ec2a196bfe1d347370bdc2edc7d186151710b","tid":1377290,"uid":217478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"728遮打花園現場 (3)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377729\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377729</a>"},{"pid":"bd4718b7f90e05f2335c08e438c3f16f6cfe2ef5","tid":1377290,"uid":237355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11db2c752fbde18e6ddf649d8c57e40ab4558a5","tid":1377290,"uid":23966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"997fec32de0858621e584eb26af17889f505cc59","tid":1377290,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路。<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，但係咁先要做多啲文宣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n做多啲文宣係香港獨立，不過要soft啲可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0b7b22ffc81f7311361c465864871e160bffc6","tid":1377290,"uid":114553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"